cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with video summarization, which is a task related to visual content analysis. The use of deep learning and reinforcement learning also suggests that it could belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories. Multimedia (cs.MM) and Information Retrieval (cs.IR) are also possible categories as video summarization is a task related to multimedia content and information retrieval.
